The paper proposes a model for generating lead sheets using recurrent neural networks, which falls under the broad category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The model involves generating harmonic and rhythmic templates, which suggests a focus on music information retrieval (cs.SD) and sequence modeling (cs.SI). The use of LSTM-based models also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG).
